    "title": "京东开放平台商品水效标识展示信息合规规范",
    "followRuleId": "1298601922258026496",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第一章</span> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">概述</span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第一条</span> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">适用范围</span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">本规范适用于京东商家。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第二条</span> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">相关定义</span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">（一）水效标识：依据《水效标识管理办法》相关规定，水效标识是指采用企业自我声明和信息备案的方式，表示用水产品水效等级等性能的一种符合性标志。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">（二）水效标识的实施：依据《水效标识管理办法》相关规定，凡列入</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;《中华人民共和国实行水效标识的产品目录》中的产品在网络交易中应当在产品信息展示主页面醒目位置展示相应的水效标识。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第二章</span> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">水效标识展示要求</span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第三条</span> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">展示内容</span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><a name=\"_Hlk110363025\"></a><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">水效标识应当包括以下基本内容：</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">（一）中文名称</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&ldquo;中国水效标识&rdquo;；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">（二）英文名称</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">China Water Efficiency Label；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">（三）生产者名称或者简称；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">（四）产品规格型号；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">（五）水效等级；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">（六）水效指标；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">（七）依据的水效强制性国家标准编号；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">（八）水效信息码。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">列入国家水效</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&ldquo;领跑者&rdquo;目录的产品，还应当包括水效&ldquo;领跑者&rdquo;相关信息。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第四条</span> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">展示位置：</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">主图（建议放置辅图最后一张）。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第五条</span> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">展示形式：</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">标识平面图或产品实物图。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第六条</span> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">展示示例：</span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-size: 10pt;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" src=\"//img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/344379/40/16325/41567/68fa0b0bF91b5629e/bb82d07601d76302.png\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第三章</span> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">其他注意事项</span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第七条</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">商品标题、广告语、主图、基本信息、参数属性、详情页等页面模块涉及水效等级信息填写描述需与产品水效标识里的信息保持一致，禁止出现填写信息不一致的情况。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第八条</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">套装组合商品需分别一一展示每件产品的水效标识图片。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第九条</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">上传的水效标识信息应当字迹清晰，容易辨认识读，禁止篡改原标识内容信息。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第四章</span> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">违规处理</span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第十条</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">对于违反相关法律法规及本规范的商家，京东有权依据协议及</span></span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2754&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><u><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》</span></span></u></a><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">采取处理措施。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第五章</span> <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">附则</span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第十一条</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;京东可根据运营情况随时调整本规范并以公告的形式向商家公示。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第十二条</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;若涉及特殊商品的，除满足本规范要求外，仍须符合特殊商品相关规则。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第十三条</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等的规定。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等的行为，本规则已有规定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无规定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 2; background: #ffffff; text-align: left; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第十四条</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 200%; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;本规则于2022年8月5日发布，于2022年8月12日生效。</span></span></span></p>",
